{"id": "1005722", "question": " X,Y 独立并且，X~U(0,2)以及Y∼U(1,3)。求max(X,Y) 的期望。", "description": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">已知 X,Y 独立并且分别服从不同的均匀分布。X∼U(0,2) 以及Y∼U(1,3)。求 max(X,Y) 的期望。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">这道题我问了三个人给了三个答案。求大家帮忙。谢谢！<br/></span><br/></p></div>", "viewer": 4134, "tags": ["统计/机器学习", "概率分布"], "answers": [{"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>令$Z=max(X,Y)$, 作图如下。</p><p><img data-filename=\"image.png\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 204px;\"/></p><p>可以看到红色区域的mean=1.5，紫色mean=2.5，蓝色mean=2.5，</p><p>绿色mean= $\\int_{1}^{2}\\int_{x}^{2}ydydx=5/3$</p><p>橙色mean= $\\int_{1}^{2}\\int_{y}^{2}xdxdy=5/3$</p><p>整体mean=$(1.5+2.5+2.5+5/3*0.5+5/3*0.5)/4=2.04$</p><pre><code class=\"python\">import numpy as np\nn=100000\nx = np.random.uniform(0, 2,n)\ny = np.random.uniform(1, 3,n)\nz=np.maximum(x,y)\nprint(np.mean(z))</code></pre><p>2.0405704490035905</p></div>", "lvl2_answer": []}, {"lvl1_answer": "<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-10 p-r\"><p>偷懒做个模拟</p><pre><code class=\"python\">import numpy as np\nx = np.random.uniform(0, 2, 1000000)\ny = np.random.uniform(1, 3, 1000000)\nprint(np.mean(np.max([x, y], axis=0)))</code></pre><p>得到的结果是2.041519543743509</p></div>", "lvl2_answer": ["之前我代码错了，现在改了一下"]}]}